    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390130/extras/5c47757785bc9ba4e7c731bcf5734c2e.poster.avif?t=1770782318\" width=800 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390130/extras/5c47757785bc9ba4e7c731bcf5734c2e.webm?t=1770782318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390130/extras/5c47757785bc9ba4e7c731bcf5734c2e.mp4?t=1770782318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款温馨的室内装饰游戏里，你将扮演刚从大学毕业的年轻女巫达莉娅。按照自己的喜好打扫装点精美空间的同时，你还要帮助小镇及居住在此的魔法生物们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390130/extras/7ada2d9762bf4742556e8cbd243a105e.poster.avif?t=1770782318\" width=800 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390130/extras/7ada2d9762bf4742556e8cbd243a105e.webm?t=1770782318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390130/extras/7ada2d9762bf4742556e8cbd243a105e.mp4?t=1770782318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随心装点：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸于没有计时器的放松玩法，按自己的节奏布置空间。运用魔法微调色彩、尺寸与魔法特效，打造最温馨的居所。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390130/extras/2dda6bf4cfd171d11a073cae156f59bf.avif?t=1770782318\" width=616 height=279 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结识女巫团体：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与镇民交谈，在打扫装饰店铺的过程中了解他们的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390130/extras/c2d7a2143bc698c4a011850b2a48cc7b.poster.avif?t=1770782318\" width=800 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390130/extras/c2d7a2143bc698c4a011850b2a48cc7b.webm?t=1770782318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390130/extras/c2d7a2143bc698c4a011850b2a48cc7b.mp4?t=1770782318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >救助生灵：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >帮助受神秘腐化影响的魔法生物，用爱心探寻灾厄根源。 💖</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390130/extras/592d0c94cbfa18f8552fb99eb8311478.poster.avif?t=1770782318\" width=612 height=596 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390130/extras/592d0c94cbfa18f8552fb99eb8311478.webm?t=1770782318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390130/extras/592d0c94cbfa18f8552fb99eb8311478.mp4?t=1770782318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创造模式：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有房间、家具及数百种物件任你调配！尽情发挥创意，构筑梦想中的魔法空间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特色系统：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔮 故事模式 - 通过装点多个+C21域来帮助小镇复苏</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎨 创造模式 - 数百种素材触手可及，打造专属魔法空间</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌱 自由装饰 - 依照个人喜好定制每个房间，在完成任务时展现独特风格</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧸 舒适画风 - 在可自定义天气中聆听低保真音乐，感受宁静氛围</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧿 冥想式玩法 - 无计时器的放松体验，随心掌控游戏节奏</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
